1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:01:00,000
(Watch on www.dramacool.club Support Admin)

2
00:01:37,920 --> 00:01:41,020
[The Epoch of Miyu]

3
00:01:41,130 --> 00:01:43,970
[Episode 23]

4
00:01:52,780 --> 00:01:54,370
See? What did I tell you?

5
00:01:57,410 --> 00:01:58,340
Ming,

6
00:01:59,080 --> 00:02:00,340
what's wrong with you?

7
00:02:03,690 --> 00:02:04,690
Are you okay?

8
00:02:06,540 --> 00:02:07,720
He's choking.

9
00:02:08,070 --> 00:02:08,960
What's wrong?

10
00:02:09,020 --> 00:02:10,370
I think he's choking.

11
00:02:10,400 --> 00:02:11,420
Are you choking on food?

12
00:02:11,420 --> 00:02:11,910
Right?

13
00:02:12,810 --> 00:02:13,710
What should we do?

14
00:02:13,710 --> 00:02:14,520
Here, let me help.

15
00:02:14,520 --> 00:02:15,080
How are you?

16
00:02:15,080 --> 00:02:15,770
Get up.

17
00:02:15,820 --> 00:02:16,450
Slowly.

18
00:02:17,470 --> 00:02:18,840
-How are you?
-Let me help you.

19
00:02:18,840 --> 00:02:20,170
I'll help you get it out.

20
00:02:20,430 --> 00:02:21,810
Ready? One, two, three.

21
00:02:22,430 --> 00:02:25,360
One, two, three.

22
00:02:26,860 --> 00:02:28,100
How are you?

23
00:02:29,390 --> 00:02:30,430
Sit down first.

24
00:02:30,460 --> 00:02:32,100
Come on, slowly.

25
00:02:33,960 --> 00:02:35,570
You scared me to death.

26
00:02:36,770 --> 00:02:37,460
Just now,

27
00:02:38,579 --> 00:02:39,540
it felt like

28
00:02:41,290 --> 00:02:43,470
my whole life flashed before my eyes.

29
00:02:43,650 --> 00:02:44,530
A life flashback?

30
00:02:44,530 --> 00:02:45,560
You...

31
00:02:45,579 --> 00:02:47,610
You practically got
a second chance at life.

32
00:02:47,610 --> 00:02:48,400
Ming,

33
00:02:48,610 --> 00:02:49,340
are you okay?

34
00:02:49,460 --> 00:02:50,520
Are you okay or not?

35
00:02:50,710 --> 00:02:51,640
I'm fine.

36
00:02:52,170 --> 00:02:53,360
I'm fine now.

37
00:02:54,070 --> 00:02:55,110
Thank you,

38
00:02:55,410 --> 00:02:56,250
Mr. Ji.

39
00:02:56,280 --> 00:02:58,079
It's nothing. Glad you're okay.

40
00:02:58,460 --> 00:02:59,700
Are you really okay?

41
00:03:01,580 --> 00:03:02,370
Yes.

42
00:03:03,070 --> 00:03:03,980
Of course I am.

43
00:03:05,930 --> 00:03:07,950
I don't think you are.

44
00:03:08,190 --> 00:03:09,790
You'd better go to
the hospital for a checkup.

45
00:03:09,790 --> 00:03:11,770
You still need to go to the hospital
for a further checkup.

46
00:03:11,770 --> 00:03:13,380
You can't take this lightly.

47
00:03:13,770 --> 00:03:14,730
-I'll send him there.
-Come on.

48
00:03:14,730 --> 00:03:15,660
Come, slowly.

49
00:03:16,570 --> 00:03:17,130
Slowly.

50
00:03:17,420 --> 00:03:18,100
Let's go.

51
00:03:19,740 --> 00:03:20,360
Can you do it?

52
00:03:20,360 --> 00:03:20,980
Leave it to me.

53
00:03:20,980 --> 00:03:21,470
Okay.

54
00:03:23,150 --> 00:03:24,060
Wait for me.

55
00:03:24,360 --> 00:03:25,490
I'll be right back.

56
00:03:25,520 --> 00:03:26,610
-I'll wait for you.
-Be careful.

57
00:03:26,610 --> 00:03:28,010
Hurry up and get checked.

58
00:03:28,670 --> 00:03:29,630
It's not like we're playing mahjong—

59
00:03:29,630 --> 00:03:31,160
we're not waiting for a fourth player.

60
00:03:31,160 --> 00:03:32,150
What happened?

61
00:03:32,180 --> 00:03:33,310
The old man choked.

62
00:03:33,329 --> 00:03:34,170
I'm taking him to the hospital.

63
00:03:34,170 --> 00:03:35,030
Be careful on the way.

64
00:03:35,030 --> 00:03:35,380
Okay.

65
00:03:35,530 --> 00:03:36,310
Go quickly.

66
00:03:41,000 --> 00:03:43,290
Are there any other solutions?

67
00:03:43,630 --> 00:03:45,020
I'll make some calls to find someone.

68
00:03:45,020 --> 00:03:45,970
Now?

69
00:03:46,240 --> 00:03:47,550
It's too late for a last-minute effort.

70
00:03:47,550 --> 00:03:49,160
We haven't worked together before.

71
00:03:49,160 --> 00:03:50,320
How can we perform?

72
00:03:52,530 --> 00:03:54,790
Can the performance still go as planned?

73
00:03:55,120 --> 00:03:57,680
Ms. Xu, the guests are about to enter.

74
00:03:58,030 --> 00:03:58,750
Copy that.

75
00:04:00,050 --> 00:04:02,180
Take care of the guests outside first.

76
00:04:02,940 --> 00:04:04,340
What about the band?

77
00:04:05,210 --> 00:04:06,280
Leave the band

78
00:04:06,460 --> 00:04:07,300
to me.

79
00:04:07,980 --> 00:04:08,710
Don't worry.

80
00:04:09,480 --> 00:04:10,280
I've got this.

81
00:04:13,900 --> 00:04:16,380
[Lusia University 60th Anniversary]

82
00:04:29,810 --> 00:04:31,610
Hello. Please come in.

83
00:04:38,050 --> 00:04:39,330
Ms. Dianjiangchun.

84
00:04:41,310 --> 00:04:43,520
It's me. I heard your hotel

85
00:04:43,540 --> 00:04:45,300
has a jazz performance tonight.

86
00:04:45,300 --> 00:04:46,620
I just came to join the fun.

87
00:04:46,620 --> 00:04:47,800
Let me find you a seat.

88
00:04:47,800 --> 00:04:48,350
Follow me.

89
00:04:48,350 --> 00:04:48,950
Thank you.

90
00:04:58,330 --> 00:04:59,550
This is a good seat.

91
00:05:01,540 --> 00:05:02,600
Please have a seat.

92
00:05:07,070 --> 00:05:07,900
It's okay.

93
00:05:08,850 --> 00:05:09,440
Thank you.

94
00:05:09,440 --> 00:05:10,030
It's fine.

95
00:05:10,030 --> 00:05:11,490
Go do your work. Don't worry about me.

96
00:05:11,490 --> 00:05:13,290
Let me know if you need anything.

97
00:05:32,520 --> 00:05:33,409
Miyu.

98
00:05:34,620 --> 00:05:35,659
Chairman Wei.

99
00:05:36,260 --> 00:05:38,360
The decoration has quite a nice vibe.

100
00:05:39,080 --> 00:05:41,210
How did the rehearsal go this morning?

101
00:05:41,500 --> 00:05:44,330
Those old guys won't
sing out of tune, will they?

102
00:05:44,350 --> 00:05:45,350
They...

103
00:05:46,330 --> 00:05:47,180
They are here.

104
00:05:54,460 --> 00:05:56,000
Please take a seat here.

105
00:06:10,860 --> 00:06:18,060
[Lusia University 60th Anniversary]

106
00:06:22,370 --> 00:06:23,470
[Lusia University 60th Anniversary]

107
00:06:31,050 --> 00:06:34,460
[Lusia University 60th Anniversary]

108
00:09:14,900 --> 00:09:20,390
[Lusia University 60th Anniversary]

109
00:09:55,520 --> 00:09:57,390
Do you want to watch our performance too?

110
00:09:57,390 --> 00:09:58,550
Yes. Can we?

111
00:09:58,580 --> 00:09:59,450
Of course.

112
00:09:59,470 --> 00:10:00,040
Come.

113
00:10:00,110 --> 00:10:00,830
Thank you.

114
00:10:01,130 --> 00:10:02,130
This way, please.

115
00:10:05,850 --> 00:10:06,620
Sit here.

116
00:10:07,710 --> 00:10:09,050
You can stay here.

117
00:10:39,030 --> 00:10:40,790
Thank you, Mr. Ji,

118
00:10:40,790 --> 00:10:41,560
for saving us.

119
00:10:41,560 --> 00:10:43,090
Here's to our cooperation.

120
00:10:51,900 --> 00:10:52,790
Thank you.

121
00:10:55,000 --> 00:10:56,360
What does it say?

122
00:10:56,740 --> 00:10:57,790
Let's see.

123
00:11:01,780 --> 00:11:02,870
Ji Feng.

124
00:11:04,890 --> 00:11:05,910
Thank you.

125
00:11:21,160 --> 00:11:22,000
[A jazz performance by Shanghai's
old-school gentlemen]

126
00:11:22,020 --> 00:11:22,830
[Old Shanghai jazz performance]

127
00:11:22,850 --> 00:11:23,660
[Uncles' jazz music]

128
00:11:23,690 --> 00:11:24,800
[The most stylish in Shanghai]

129
00:11:26,210 --> 00:11:26,530
[Comments]

130
00:11:26,550 --> 00:11:27,210
[Where is this show?]

131
00:11:27,210 --> 00:11:27,570
[Everyone, this is the jazz performance
at Purong Hotel]

132
00:11:27,570 --> 00:11:27,800
[The guy in the white suit
playing saxophone is so handsome]

133
00:11:27,800 --> 00:11:28,390
[I didn't know jazz could sound this good]

134
00:11:28,390 --> 00:11:28,970
[Purong is amazing]

135
00:11:28,970 --> 00:11:29,360
[Ahhh, I'm here live—
the location is Purong Hotel]

136
00:11:29,380 --> 00:11:29,630
[Everyone, hurry and come!]

137
00:11:29,660 --> 00:11:30,240
[I'm so happy.]

138
00:11:30,240 --> 00:11:30,630
[It's nice.]

139
00:11:30,670 --> 00:11:31,710
[Purong Hotel jazz performance
recap is here]

140
00:11:31,770 --> 00:11:32,180
[A reunion after sixty years,
an unforgettable night]

141
00:11:32,240 --> 00:11:32,980
[Meiling's life]

142
00:11:33,000 --> 00:11:33,440
[Sort by popularity]

143
00:11:33,470 --> 00:11:33,730
[Come copy this idea together]

144
00:11:33,800 --> 00:11:34,940
[Purong Hotel's senior jazz performance
is going viral!]

145
00:11:43,260 --> 00:11:44,260
Take care.

146
00:11:44,730 --> 00:11:45,330
Okay.

147
00:11:45,410 --> 00:11:46,370
Goodbye.

148
00:11:46,710 --> 00:11:47,400
Goodbye.

149
00:11:47,510 --> 00:11:48,050
Goodbye.

150
00:11:48,080 --> 00:11:49,150
We will meet again.

151
00:11:49,150 --> 00:11:50,200
Definitely, we will meet again.

152
00:11:50,200 --> 00:11:50,630
Bye.

153
00:11:50,650 --> 00:11:51,080
Bye.

154
00:11:51,110 --> 00:11:51,750
Bye. Bye.

155
00:11:51,750 --> 00:11:52,600
Goodbye.

156
00:11:57,210 --> 00:11:58,250
Daniel,

157
00:11:59,090 --> 00:12:01,490
congratulations
on your successful performance.

158
00:12:01,490 --> 00:12:02,450
Thank you.

159
00:12:05,260 --> 00:12:08,850
This is just a beautiful dream.

160
00:12:11,320 --> 00:12:12,590
What a nice dream.

161
00:12:13,770 --> 00:12:14,810
It is a good dream.

162
00:12:15,400 --> 00:12:16,730
But wouldn't it be great

163
00:12:17,440 --> 00:12:19,440
if we could

164
00:12:21,090 --> 00:12:22,750
never wake up from this dream?

165
00:12:44,330 --> 00:12:46,130
Come to the Western restaurant.

166
00:12:46,850 --> 00:12:48,600
Although the reaction was good today,

167
00:12:48,600 --> 00:12:51,240
there are still many areas to improve.

168
00:12:51,660 --> 00:12:53,530
I saw everyone really
enjoyed your performance.

169
00:12:53,530 --> 00:12:55,190
Please give me more feedback.

170
00:12:55,350 --> 00:12:56,370
Mr. Ji, you were looking for me?

171
00:12:56,370 --> 00:12:56,980
Yes.

172
00:12:58,020 --> 00:12:59,880
Aren't you going to introduce us?

173
00:12:59,880 --> 00:13:02,240
This is our lobby manager, Xu Miyu,

174
00:13:02,440 --> 00:13:03,990
and she is also the person in charge

175
00:13:03,990 --> 00:13:05,320
of the concert tonight.

176
00:13:06,290 --> 00:13:07,020
This is...

177
00:13:07,050 --> 00:13:08,290
Ms. Dianjiangchun,

178
00:13:09,020 --> 00:13:10,550
I'm a big fan of yours.

179
00:13:11,010 --> 00:13:12,920
Really? Thank you for your attention.

180
00:13:12,920 --> 00:13:14,320
My name is Jiang Zhichun.

181
00:13:15,520 --> 00:13:17,720
Tonight's concert was really amazing.

182
00:13:18,120 --> 00:13:19,160
Especially since

183
00:13:19,300 --> 00:13:20,450
I didn't expect Mr. Ji

184
00:13:20,450 --> 00:13:21,880
to have such talent.

185
00:13:22,470 --> 00:13:24,950
Seriously, consider
appearing on my channel.

186
00:13:24,950 --> 00:13:26,310
I will definitely turn you into

187
00:13:26,310 --> 00:13:27,700
a superstar of the hotel industry.

188
00:13:27,700 --> 00:13:28,460
No,

189
00:13:28,480 --> 00:13:29,940
please don't joke with me.

190
00:13:30,640 --> 00:13:32,470
You guys can talk.

191
00:13:32,620 --> 00:13:33,500
We'll be in touch later.

192
00:13:33,500 --> 00:13:33,980
Okay.

193
00:13:34,400 --> 00:13:35,520
I'll walk you out.

194
00:13:35,550 --> 00:13:37,280
It's fine, you guys talk.

195
00:13:38,290 --> 00:13:39,420
Alright, take care.

196
00:13:44,300 --> 00:13:45,690
Have a seat.

197
00:13:52,670 --> 00:13:53,550
Try this.

198
00:14:06,930 --> 00:14:08,280
What do you think of this place?

199
00:14:08,280 --> 00:14:09,810
I want to hear your opinion.

200
00:14:11,300 --> 00:14:12,180
I think

201
00:14:12,920 --> 00:14:15,610
the equipment is pretty complete.

202
00:14:16,130 --> 00:14:17,050
But

203
00:14:17,390 --> 00:14:18,950
it lacks refinement.

204
00:14:19,120 --> 00:14:21,180
Take these snacks for example. Look,

205
00:14:21,280 --> 00:14:23,040
they're barely touched on the tables.

206
00:14:23,040 --> 00:14:24,440
An amateur setup, right?

207
00:14:24,640 --> 00:14:26,330
I didn't say that.

208
00:14:26,470 --> 00:14:28,020
I think you're absolutely right.

209
00:14:28,020 --> 00:14:29,290
We're on the same page.

210
00:14:29,990 --> 00:14:31,380
Next, I want to

211
00:14:31,810 --> 00:14:33,340
upgrade this amateur setup

212
00:14:34,120 --> 00:14:37,120
and make it a truly
high-class performance venue.

213
00:14:37,230 --> 00:14:38,230
What do you mean?

214
00:14:38,250 --> 00:14:39,780
Didn't you hear what I said?

215
00:14:40,450 --> 00:14:43,310
You want to continue the performances
in the Western restaurant?

216
00:14:43,310 --> 00:14:44,440
As you saw,

217
00:14:44,720 --> 00:14:46,170
tonight's performance

218
00:14:46,370 --> 00:14:48,250
actually had a really good response.

219
00:14:48,250 --> 00:14:49,580
So I decided

220
00:14:49,720 --> 00:14:51,320
that the next performance

221
00:14:51,600 --> 00:14:53,010
will be this Friday.

222
00:14:53,040 --> 00:14:54,490
If Daniel finds out,

223
00:14:54,520 --> 00:14:55,760
he'll be thrilled.

224
00:14:57,420 --> 00:14:59,270
But I have other considerations.

225
00:14:59,270 --> 00:15:00,320
Daniel's band

226
00:15:00,320 --> 00:15:02,030
has an average age of over 70.

227
00:15:02,320 --> 00:15:04,030
It's good. It's a selling point.

228
00:15:04,030 --> 00:15:05,830
But at the same time, it's a risk.

229
00:15:07,040 --> 00:15:07,970
Isn't this

230
00:15:08,230 --> 00:15:10,520
exactly the value of Mr. Ji?

231
00:15:11,710 --> 00:15:13,970
Health issues at an advanced age
are indeed a pain point,

232
00:15:13,970 --> 00:15:17,210
but if we manage the risks well,

233
00:15:17,360 --> 00:15:19,170
this pain point can also become

234
00:15:19,200 --> 00:15:21,200
a rare highlight and selling point.

235
00:15:21,230 --> 00:15:22,630
What do you think, Mr. Ji?

236
00:15:23,400 --> 00:15:25,400
You're leaving this question to me.

237
00:15:27,870 --> 00:15:30,140
So you were testing me.

238
00:15:31,030 --> 00:15:33,430
So what kind of answer
do you want to give me?

239
00:15:34,900 --> 00:15:36,240
Every close call without disaster

240
00:15:36,240 --> 00:15:37,810
helps us rise to the next level.

241
00:15:37,810 --> 00:15:38,580
So,

242
00:15:38,640 --> 00:15:41,090
I won't be scared off by a minor accident.

243
00:15:41,240 --> 00:15:43,430
After all, people always aim higher.

244
00:15:46,700 --> 00:15:47,500
Then,

245
00:15:48,030 --> 00:15:51,510
how about you and I share the risks

246
00:15:52,020 --> 00:15:52,900
together?

247
00:15:54,910 --> 00:15:56,320
I think the performances here

248
00:15:56,320 --> 00:15:57,790
can continue long-term,

249
00:15:58,070 --> 00:15:59,380
but on one condition—

250
00:15:59,410 --> 00:16:01,620
I want the person managing them

251
00:16:01,640 --> 00:16:02,430
to be you.

252
00:16:03,640 --> 00:16:04,480
Me?

253
00:16:04,920 --> 00:16:05,560
Yes.

254
00:16:06,800 --> 00:16:08,680
Really, I need you.

255
00:16:20,900 --> 00:16:21,530
[Party A: Purong Hotel Co., Ltd.]

256
00:16:21,550 --> 00:16:22,560
[Party B: Daniel and his friends' band]

257
00:16:24,630 --> 00:16:25,350
Really?

258
00:16:26,670 --> 00:16:27,150
Yes.

259
00:16:27,270 --> 00:16:28,010
Yes.

260
00:16:28,030 --> 00:16:28,880
Really.

261
00:16:29,440 --> 00:16:30,080
Really.

262
00:16:30,110 --> 00:16:31,020
Yes!

263
00:16:35,040 --> 00:16:36,570
You were right to come back.

264
00:17:11,339 --> 00:17:18,540
[Daniel and his friends]

265
00:17:19,349 --> 00:17:20,400
Attention, everyone.

266
00:17:20,400 --> 00:17:21,589
Starting today,

267
00:17:21,589 --> 00:17:24,040
Ms. Xu will not only be our lobby manager,

268
00:17:24,060 --> 00:17:26,380
but she will also work
at the jazz bar at night.

269
00:17:26,380 --> 00:17:27,609
So please be understanding.

270
00:17:27,609 --> 00:17:28,870
If you can solve a problem yourselves,

271
00:17:28,870 --> 00:17:30,670
don't always bother Ms. Xu.

272
00:17:30,800 --> 00:17:31,560
All right.

273
00:17:33,300 --> 00:17:34,130
Back to work.

274
00:17:38,200 --> 00:17:39,800
How impressive can she be?

275
00:17:39,990 --> 00:17:41,870
At work, she's juggling two jobs at once.

276
00:17:41,870 --> 00:17:43,800
Well, she's got powerful backing.

277
00:17:45,660 --> 00:17:50,780
[Purong Hotel]

278
00:17:49,300 --> 00:17:51,430
Lu Xiaoyan, make three copies of this.

279
00:18:50,160 --> 00:18:51,220
What are you doing?

280
00:18:51,220 --> 00:18:54,080
In broad daylight,
you're giving me a heart attack?

281
00:18:57,430 --> 00:18:58,280
Come up.

282
00:19:07,640 --> 00:19:10,360
Director Bai, ever since I joined Purong

283
00:19:10,390 --> 00:19:12,820
and the Front Office,
I've been working under you.

284
00:19:12,820 --> 00:19:15,390
You know how much overtime I've worked

285
00:19:15,420 --> 00:19:17,230
and how many all-nighters I've pulled.

286
00:19:17,230 --> 00:19:18,180
But what happened?

287
00:19:18,180 --> 00:19:20,030
Xu Miyu came out of nowhere,

288
00:19:20,590 --> 00:19:23,110
stole my lobby manager position.

289
00:19:23,130 --> 00:19:25,480
She's holding onto the jazz bar too.

290
00:19:25,680 --> 00:19:26,720
Why does Xu Miyu get

291
00:19:26,720 --> 00:19:28,400
all the benefits to herself?

292
00:19:28,400 --> 00:19:29,750
Why?

293
00:19:30,000 --> 00:19:32,270
You didn't say a single word for me.

294
00:19:33,320 --> 00:19:34,120
Don't cry.

295
00:19:35,680 --> 00:19:36,160
Alright.

296
00:19:36,160 --> 00:19:37,200
Stop crying.

297
00:19:37,290 --> 00:19:39,500
I highly recognize your ability,

298
00:19:39,620 --> 00:19:41,420
and I feel it's unfair to you too.

299
00:19:41,880 --> 00:19:43,560
But the way Xu Miyu does things

300
00:19:43,580 --> 00:19:45,390
is truly flawless.

301
00:19:45,890 --> 00:19:47,550
Besides, she has
the general manager's backing.

302
00:19:47,550 --> 00:19:48,700
What am I supposed to do?

303
00:19:48,700 --> 00:19:50,600
Then what do you want me to do?

304
00:19:50,630 --> 00:19:51,740
You make empty promises all day

305
00:19:51,740 --> 00:19:53,230
without giving anything practical.

306
00:19:53,230 --> 00:19:54,740
Should I even keep working here?

307
00:19:54,740 --> 00:19:56,480
Are you asking me
to fight a losing battle?

308
00:19:56,480 --> 00:19:58,630
If I can't survive here,
who will promote you?

309
00:19:58,630 --> 00:19:59,480
But I...

310
00:19:59,500 --> 00:20:01,360
Cut the crap and get out of the car.

311
00:20:03,200 --> 00:20:04,160
Get out!

312
00:20:26,750 --> 00:20:27,430
Wait.

313
00:20:27,450 --> 00:20:29,540
The height of that light is wrong.

314
00:20:29,900 --> 00:20:32,140
Move the whole chandelier up

315
00:20:32,170 --> 00:20:33,430
by about a meter, okay?

316
00:20:33,650 --> 00:20:35,230
Alright, let's step it up, everyone.

317
00:20:35,230 --> 00:20:35,880
Hurry up.

318
00:20:35,920 --> 00:20:36,510
Okay.

319
00:20:36,510 --> 00:20:37,400
Mr. Ji.

320
00:20:43,750 --> 00:20:44,560
Mr. Duan.

321
00:20:45,590 --> 00:20:46,850
The stage looks great.

322
00:20:47,040 --> 00:20:49,100
You really know how to spend my money.

323
00:20:50,330 --> 00:20:52,390
You have to spend money to make money.

324
00:20:52,610 --> 00:20:53,940
What's wrong, Mr. Duan?

325
00:20:54,370 --> 00:20:56,330
Why didn't you find a comfortable place

326
00:20:56,330 --> 00:20:57,660
instead of coming here?

327
00:20:57,990 --> 00:20:59,390
I'm on-site inspection.

328
00:20:59,830 --> 00:21:02,160
Did you think I was just pampered?

329
00:21:09,770 --> 00:21:11,430
The tableware doesn't match.

330
00:21:14,870 --> 00:21:15,920
The cooking is bad too.

331
00:21:15,920 --> 00:21:17,440
Brother, come help out.

332
00:21:17,510 --> 00:21:17,970
Hurry up and help.

333
00:21:17,970 --> 00:21:18,860
Waiter!

334
00:21:20,600 --> 00:21:21,430
Waiter!

335
00:21:24,230 --> 00:21:25,320
Waiter!

336
00:21:27,480 --> 00:21:29,210
The service is a total mess too.

337
00:21:29,360 --> 00:21:31,060
How can you expect me to trust you,

338
00:21:31,060 --> 00:21:31,780
Mr. Ji?

339
00:21:32,750 --> 00:21:33,480
Mr. Duan,

340
00:21:33,600 --> 00:21:36,500
you need to
trust your own investment vision.

341
00:21:36,530 --> 00:21:37,750
But when I invested,

342
00:21:37,750 --> 00:21:39,480
I didn't expect you would come.

343
00:21:41,460 --> 00:21:42,460
Surprise.

344
00:21:44,090 --> 00:21:45,790
Do you know what they said

345
00:21:45,790 --> 00:21:46,960
when the Jazz Bar project was approved

346
00:21:46,960 --> 00:21:47,790
by the board?

347
00:21:47,960 --> 00:21:48,960
What did they say?

348
00:21:49,200 --> 00:21:50,360
Flashy but impractical,

349
00:21:50,360 --> 00:21:51,640
with short-term effects.

350
00:21:51,640 --> 00:21:52,940
You worked your heart out

351
00:21:52,940 --> 00:21:54,310
for the whole hotel,

352
00:21:54,610 --> 00:21:56,610
but they don't appreciate it at all.

353
00:21:57,000 --> 00:21:59,060
I don't need anyone's appreciation.

354
00:21:59,360 --> 00:22:00,470
I'm just doing what

355
00:22:00,680 --> 00:22:02,710
a hotel general manager should do.

356
00:22:06,100 --> 00:22:07,050
Mr. Duan,

357
00:22:07,410 --> 00:22:09,410
when our jazz bar opens,

358
00:22:09,440 --> 00:22:11,700
do you want me
to save a few tables for you?

359
00:22:18,010 --> 00:22:18,900
Just this?

360
00:22:19,640 --> 00:22:21,920
I think you should forget about it.

361
00:22:27,380 --> 00:22:29,240
You are definitely going to lose.

362
00:22:30,070 --> 00:22:31,400
I will accept my defeat.

363
00:22:34,290 --> 00:22:35,050
Take care.

364
00:22:50,120 --> 00:22:51,950
Didn't you go see Duan Aoxiang?

365
00:22:52,150 --> 00:22:54,010
He invited you for afternoon tea?

366
00:23:01,160 --> 00:23:02,880
Duan Aoxiang is right.

367
00:23:03,330 --> 00:23:05,240
Before our jazz bar opens,

368
00:23:05,620 --> 00:23:07,220
we must get our refreshments

369
00:23:07,290 --> 00:23:08,320
sorted out quickly.

370
00:23:08,320 --> 00:23:10,120
And stop restocking

371
00:23:10,240 --> 00:23:11,240
that durian puff.

372
00:23:11,850 --> 00:23:12,400
Okay.

373
00:23:13,400 --> 00:23:14,510
By the way,

374
00:23:14,750 --> 00:23:16,580
you and this VIP Chun
have been interacting a lot

375
00:23:16,580 --> 00:23:17,520
and chatting quite happily.

376
00:23:17,520 --> 00:23:19,680
She called again
to ask about your schedule.

377
00:23:19,680 --> 00:23:21,000
What VIP Chun?

378
00:23:23,900 --> 00:23:27,470
[Jiang Zhichun]

379
00:23:26,430 --> 00:23:27,750
I have a new idea.

380
00:23:27,770 --> 00:23:29,740
Let's have dinner tonight and talk.

381
00:23:29,740 --> 00:23:30,670
I'll pick you up.

382
00:23:30,800 --> 00:23:31,800
Stop pretending.

383
00:23:32,890 --> 00:23:34,240
I have a feeling

384
00:23:34,360 --> 00:23:35,540
that she may not necessarily

385
00:23:35,540 --> 00:23:37,540
be coming for our Purong Hotel.

386
00:23:37,960 --> 00:23:39,170
Dianjiangchun is indeed

387
00:23:39,170 --> 00:23:41,050
a valued patron of our Purong Hotel.

388
00:23:41,050 --> 00:23:42,580
No matter what she's after,

389
00:23:43,160 --> 00:23:45,020
as long as it's a win-win situation,

390
00:23:45,020 --> 00:23:46,700
we should do our best to cooperate.

391
00:23:46,700 --> 00:23:48,610
What if she takes advantage of work

392
00:23:48,610 --> 00:23:50,610
to talk to you about something else?

393
00:23:52,770 --> 00:23:53,920
Outside of work,

394
00:23:54,730 --> 00:23:55,530
we

395
00:23:56,420 --> 00:23:58,220
have nothing else to talk about.

396
00:23:58,270 --> 00:23:59,070
Junior,

397
00:24:00,280 --> 00:24:02,310
do you have someone in your heart?

398
00:24:05,770 --> 00:24:06,480
Right?

399
00:24:10,250 --> 00:24:11,880
Does she know?

400
00:24:42,530 --> 00:24:43,240
Ms. Xu.

401
00:24:43,710 --> 00:24:44,780
Ms. Jiang.

402
00:24:44,930 --> 00:24:46,580
Are you here to check in?

403
00:24:46,610 --> 00:24:48,070
No, I have an appointment.

404
00:24:48,200 --> 00:24:49,450
I bought you some milk tea.

405
00:24:49,450 --> 00:24:50,870
Oh, how can I accept this?

406
00:24:51,020 --> 00:24:52,620
It's a perk for my followers.

407
00:24:52,950 --> 00:24:53,800
Take it.

408
00:24:53,830 --> 00:24:54,630
Thank you.

409
00:24:54,650 --> 00:24:55,550
Don't mention it.

410
00:24:55,550 --> 00:24:57,410
We'll be seeing each other often.

411
00:24:58,210 --> 00:24:58,810
By the way,

412
00:24:58,920 --> 00:25:01,680
why do you think milk tea

413
00:25:01,710 --> 00:25:03,560
is so appealing to young people?

414
00:25:04,600 --> 00:25:06,660
Sorry, it's an occupational hazard.

415
00:25:06,690 --> 00:25:08,310
A few milk tea shops

416
00:25:08,340 --> 00:25:09,850
have been talking to me
about partnerships lately.

417
00:25:09,850 --> 00:25:11,530
For someone

418
00:25:11,550 --> 00:25:13,150
at my age,

419
00:25:13,180 --> 00:25:14,400
I really can't tell the difference

420
00:25:14,400 --> 00:25:16,710
between the different brands.

421
00:25:17,450 --> 00:25:19,250
How do you think I should choose?

422
00:25:20,290 --> 00:25:21,570
Could it be because

423
00:25:21,590 --> 00:25:24,270
milk tea conveys
goodwill better than water?

424
00:25:24,350 --> 00:25:25,500
Not only is it sweet,

425
00:25:25,550 --> 00:25:26,870
but it's also versatile.

426
00:25:26,870 --> 00:25:28,040
You can add anything to it.

427
00:25:28,040 --> 00:25:29,170
It rejects nothing,

428
00:25:29,240 --> 00:25:30,990
which makes it a very easygoing drink.

429
00:25:30,990 --> 00:25:33,030
That's a good angle.

430
00:25:36,010 --> 00:25:36,970
My appointment is here.

431
00:25:36,970 --> 00:25:37,850
I'll get going.

432
00:25:37,870 --> 00:25:38,690
Thank you.

433
00:25:40,140 --> 00:25:40,870
Ji Feng.

434
00:25:42,030 --> 00:25:43,680
Let's find a place to talk.

435
00:25:43,720 --> 00:25:44,880
Let's go. My car is outside.

436
00:25:44,880 --> 00:25:45,740
Did you drive here?

437
00:25:45,740 --> 00:25:46,440
Then I'll ride with you.

438
00:25:46,440 --> 00:25:46,680
Let's go.

439
00:25:46,680 --> 00:25:47,200
Okay.

440
00:26:22,620 --> 00:26:24,010
I'll show you something.

441
00:26:24,010 --> 00:26:24,690
Okay.

442
00:26:33,460 --> 00:26:35,060
You've published a new book?

443
00:26:35,220 --> 00:26:36,090
Take a look. What do you think?

444
00:26:35,970 --> 00:26:36,720
[Chun's Daily Taste]

445
00:26:38,750 --> 00:26:39,930
[Chun's Daily Taste]

446
00:26:39,300 --> 00:26:39,990
It's great.

447
00:26:40,210 --> 00:26:41,610
The photos are very good.

448
00:26:42,130 --> 00:26:43,850
This is my first time publishing a book.

449
00:26:43,850 --> 00:26:46,650
It records my travels, shop explorations,

450
00:26:46,680 --> 00:26:48,090
and some food notes.

451
00:26:48,390 --> 00:26:49,450
Congratulations.

452
00:26:49,670 --> 00:26:50,270
Thank you.

453
00:26:53,980 --> 00:26:55,100
Recently, our team

454
00:26:55,120 --> 00:26:56,950
is also choosing a venue

455
00:26:56,980 --> 00:26:58,820
for the new book's signing event.

456
00:26:58,820 --> 00:27:00,370
We are dazzled by the choices,

457
00:27:00,370 --> 00:27:02,960
and the more we look,
the less satisfied we become.

458
00:27:02,960 --> 00:27:04,090
So,

459
00:27:05,360 --> 00:27:07,300
could I hold the signing event

460
00:27:07,580 --> 00:27:09,180
for my new book at your hotel?

461
00:27:11,900 --> 00:27:12,580
Of course.

462
00:27:12,610 --> 00:27:14,850
If it's not too much trouble.

463
00:27:15,430 --> 00:27:17,950
Of course. It would be our pleasure.

464
00:27:18,180 --> 00:27:18,850
Okay.

465
00:27:23,860 --> 00:27:26,120
Hello, I've decided.

466
00:27:26,440 --> 00:27:28,740
The book signing will be at Purong.

467
00:27:29,490 --> 00:27:30,820
Eliminate the others.

468
00:27:33,260 --> 00:27:35,570
Can I check out the venue next week?

469
00:27:36,200 --> 00:27:37,860
I'll be at your full disposal.

470
00:27:38,730 --> 00:27:39,120
Okay.

471
00:27:39,310 --> 00:27:40,760
Hello, your fish is ready.

472
00:27:40,760 --> 00:27:41,440
Enjoy your meal.

473
00:27:41,440 --> 00:27:42,200
Thank you.

474
00:27:42,740 --> 00:27:43,930
Try their fish.

475
00:27:43,960 --> 00:27:44,890
It's delicious.

476
00:27:45,130 --> 00:27:45,680
Okay.

477
00:27:50,820 --> 00:27:52,020
The fish is so tender.

478
00:27:52,920 --> 00:27:54,250
It really is delicious.

479
00:28:01,400 --> 00:28:03,000
It really is Dianjiangchun!

480
00:28:03,080 --> 00:28:03,610
Let's go.

481
00:28:04,910 --> 00:28:06,320
We really like you.

482
00:28:06,600 --> 00:28:08,800
Hello. I really like your videos.

483
00:28:08,820 --> 00:28:10,480
Can we take a picture with you?

484
00:28:10,540 --> 00:28:11,100
Sure.

485
00:28:12,000 --> 00:28:13,590
Sir, could you take a picture for us?

486
00:28:13,590 --> 00:28:14,310
Thank you.

487
00:28:15,680 --> 00:28:16,330
Okay.

488
00:28:17,180 --> 00:28:18,100
Okay.

489
00:28:18,130 --> 00:28:19,530
One, two, three.

490
00:28:20,240 --> 00:28:20,990
-It should be
-Thank you.

491
00:28:20,990 --> 00:28:21,800
fine.

492
00:28:21,840 --> 00:28:24,130
Are you that general manager
of Purong Hotel

493
00:28:24,130 --> 00:28:26,000
who plays the saxophone?

494
00:28:26,020 --> 00:28:27,760
I've seen you in a video.

495
00:28:27,920 --> 00:28:28,270
Hello.

496
00:28:28,270 --> 00:28:29,480
Really?

497
00:28:29,500 --> 00:28:32,010
Are you two dating?

498
00:28:32,850 --> 00:28:34,080
You misunderstood.

499
00:28:35,210 --> 00:28:37,140
Can I take a picture with you alone?

500
00:28:37,170 --> 00:28:38,450
Me too!

501
00:28:38,480 --> 00:28:41,210
-I'll take one later.
-I need to use the bathroom.

502
00:28:43,720 --> 00:28:44,510
Thank you.

503
00:28:44,510 --> 00:28:45,480
My turn!

504
00:28:51,610 --> 00:28:55,470
[Mei Restaurant]

505
00:28:53,840 --> 00:28:54,630
How is it?

506
00:28:54,650 --> 00:28:56,780
Their food tastes pretty good, right?

507
00:28:57,050 --> 00:28:58,380
It's really delicious.

508
00:28:58,860 --> 00:28:59,800
It's not easy.

509
00:29:00,160 --> 00:29:02,060
Our tastes finally align.

510
00:29:11,530 --> 00:29:12,980
You don't need to see me off.
I'll take a taxi back.

511
00:29:12,980 --> 00:29:13,890
Why?

512
00:29:17,770 --> 00:29:20,090
You're a public figure.

513
00:29:23,190 --> 00:29:25,650
Why do you have more
of an idol burden than me?

514
00:29:26,500 --> 00:29:27,800
I'm just kidding.

515
00:29:28,090 --> 00:29:30,040
You don't work in the internet ecosystem.

516
00:29:30,040 --> 00:29:32,360
So you don't understand
my work environment.

517
00:29:32,360 --> 00:29:33,560
Let's talk in the car.

518
00:29:33,770 --> 00:29:35,920
I promise you won't affect
my public image.

519
00:29:35,920 --> 00:29:36,810
Let's go.

520
00:29:36,840 --> 00:29:37,600
Okay.

521
00:29:56,390 --> 00:29:58,170
We created this Dianjiangchun persona

522
00:29:58,170 --> 00:30:00,500
in a way that naturally invites shipping—

523
00:30:01,290 --> 00:30:03,000
she's single, beautiful,

524
00:30:03,360 --> 00:30:05,120
tasteful, and romantic.

525
00:30:05,680 --> 00:30:08,040
Almost any male guest around my age

526
00:30:09,050 --> 00:30:10,050
with decent looks

527
00:30:10,160 --> 00:30:11,450
who shows up on my livestream

528
00:30:11,450 --> 00:30:14,850
ends up being pushed by the audience
as my rumored boyfriend.

529
00:30:14,960 --> 00:30:16,000
But,

530
00:30:16,030 --> 00:30:18,720
this does nothing but good for my traffic.

531
00:30:18,880 --> 00:30:21,010
The other side of traffic is scandals,

532
00:30:23,040 --> 00:30:24,040
you know?

533
00:30:24,480 --> 00:30:26,940
Being my rumored boyfriend
is not a bad deal.

534
00:30:27,030 --> 00:30:28,880
They've all become popular.

535
00:30:28,900 --> 00:30:30,070
I am very valuable.

536
00:30:32,390 --> 00:30:33,320
Thank you.

537
00:30:34,110 --> 00:30:36,920
Thank you for being willing to
help Purong Hotel.

538
00:30:39,030 --> 00:30:40,110
Is that all?

539
00:30:44,130 --> 00:30:45,610
I've arrived.

540
00:31:02,750 --> 00:31:03,440
Thank you.

541
00:31:03,560 --> 00:31:04,270
Bye.

542
00:31:08,370 --> 00:31:09,130
Ji Feng!

543
00:31:10,890 --> 00:31:12,420
When will we meet next time?

544
00:31:13,900 --> 00:31:15,730
I'll ask the PR department

545
00:31:15,760 --> 00:31:17,300
to contact your team for
your signing event.

546
00:31:17,300 --> 00:31:18,100
What about me?

547
00:31:20,060 --> 00:31:20,630
What?

548
00:31:21,090 --> 00:31:22,300
Can't I ask you out?

549
00:31:29,860 --> 00:31:31,060
Keep in touch on WeChat.

550
00:31:31,060 --> 00:31:31,820
I'm leaving.

551
00:31:32,050 --> 00:31:32,920
Bye.

552
00:31:45,970 --> 00:31:46,930
I'm off work.

553
00:31:47,020 --> 00:31:47,650
Bye.

554
00:31:47,680 --> 00:31:48,560
Bye.

555
00:31:49,040 --> 00:31:49,830
Bye.

556
00:32:31,190 --> 00:32:35,030
♪ Love is truly not easy to obtain ♪

557
00:32:38,570 --> 00:32:42,270
♪ I can't hold on to you
even if you want to leave ♪

558
00:32:45,540 --> 00:32:49,670
♪ I tell myself I'm not hurt
once things settle down ♪

559
00:32:53,180 --> 00:32:56,990
♪ but I realize I can't deceive myself ♪

560
00:33:00,560 --> 00:33:04,460
♪ I always say life is already
hard enough ♪

561
00:33:08,200 --> 00:33:12,230
♪ so what else is there worth trying for ♪

562
00:33:15,540 --> 00:33:19,580
♪ Friends comfort me,
telling me to have a drink ♪

563
00:33:23,140 --> 00:33:26,890
♪ But I've already started living
like I'm not myself anymore ♪

564
00:33:34,560 --> 00:33:38,240
Dianjiangchun's team will come to
the hotel to check the venue tomorrow.

565
00:33:38,240 --> 00:33:39,680
We must treat them

566
00:33:39,010 --> 00:33:45,340
[Purong Hotel]

567
00:33:39,680 --> 00:33:41,680
with the highest standard for VIPs.

568
00:33:41,830 --> 00:33:43,590
We must provide the service
that best reflects

569
00:33:43,590 --> 00:33:45,640
the style of Purong Hotel.

570
00:33:45,950 --> 00:33:46,920
No department

571
00:33:46,950 --> 00:33:48,430
can take chances.

572
00:33:48,820 --> 00:33:49,680
Any negligence

573
00:33:50,000 --> 00:33:52,160
will be strictly punished

574
00:33:52,160 --> 00:33:54,330
according to
the hotel's management rules.

575
00:33:54,330 --> 00:33:55,290
Director Li,

576
00:33:55,050 --> 00:33:56,270
[Purong Hotel]

577
